data.description: This 3 bed and 2 bath home offers  a lot of potential for a great family home! At 2,000 sq. ft., on the west side of Kokomo, and a backyard ready for  a garden shed and a nice deck around an above-groundpool (built in 2020). Fresh paint and updates throughout.  Other updates include roof ('21 - '22), water heater (2019), updated electrical {200 amp} (2019), and an updated laundry area equipped with Ikea cabinetry.
